OL,3,GGrampian
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FHeavy rain clearing to the east
OL,6,Fin the morning to leave a largely dry
OL,7,Fday with some bright spells and just
OL,8,Fthe odd isolated shower. Light winds
OL,9,Fat first but breezy at times in the
OL,10,Fafternoon.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FClear spells and a few
OL,13,Fshowers at first this evening. Soon
OL,14,Fturning cloudier with outbreaks of
OL,15,Frain overnight, these may be heavy at
OL,16,Ftimes. Strong winds, especially near
OL,17,Fcoasts.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
